{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 305931, "create_time": 1658372810, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "也许是镜像#86321 ", "timestamp": 1658372810}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 305942, "create_time": 1658373141, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "相信地球中心说的坏处是什么？\n", "timestamp": 1658373141}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 305958, "create_time": 1658373726, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "之前读过本尼迪克特·安德森的《民族主义的起源与散布》部分内容。一方面，对于国家的发展和一些地区的独立是有好处的，这其实就是民族主义这个概念被发明出来的一大原因。一大坏处就是急剧膨胀的民族优越感导致对外走向侵略。作者有提到日本这个世界岛边缘国家，在民族主义的帮助下完成了改革，却因为缺少协商的政治传统和视野走上了军国主义的道路。", "timestamp": 1658373726}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 305962, "create_time": 1658373936, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re Bob: 其实中国和日本非常像，甚至更甚，自认是天朝上国，自古以来就是周边小国臣服的对象。现代中国有极强的民族优越感，高度极权的政府，这些都是战争的温床。", "timestamp": 1658373936}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 306071, "create_time": 1658378942, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "有民族自豪感是正确的，但若过头，由此鄙视甚至敌视其他民族，就……", "timestamp": 1658378942}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 306094, "create_time": 1658379553, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "我觉得可能会因为沉迷在民族主义思想里然后忽略阶级问题", "timestamp": 1658379553}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 306662, "create_time": 1658400376, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Bob: 君不见网上或者树洞里如此强大的逆向民族主义。多少人认为美国好中国差，白人优等种族中国人劣等种族，哪来的民族优越感。", "timestamp": 1658400376}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 306664, "create_time": 1658400534, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Bob: 那怎么中国几十年没打仗了呢", "timestamp": 1658400534}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 306683, "create_time": 1658401131, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "坏处是吃人太多容易得阮病毒", "timestamp": 1658401131}], "create_time": 1658372787, "cw": "政治相关", "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1658401131, "likenum": 9, "n_attentions": 9, "n_comments": 9, "pid": 86325, "poll": null, "reply": 9, "text": "民族主义的坏处到底是什么？有民族自豪感、认为生养自己的这个文化是最伟大的，这种想法到底会造成哪些坏处？\n", "timestamp": 1658372787}}